data.description: Modern Oasis in Vibrant Highland Park!  Discover the perfect blend of contemporary style and spacious living at 1248 Bailey Ave. This stunning, modernized home, situated on an oversized corner lot in the desirable Highland Park neighborhood, offers a bright and airy haven waiting to be yours.  Features that excite include:  Original hardwood floors.  Open concept floor plan designed for seamless entertaining and everyday living. A sun-drenched study bathed in natural light making it the ideal work-from-home space.  Energy-saving double-pane windows.  Modern lighting and plumbing fixtures add a special touch of elegance.  A sleek kitchen boasting modern cabinetry, granite countertops, and a breakfast bar flowing into the living room.  The oversized laundry room is sure to impress with its large windows and abundance of natural lighting with views of the backyard.  Speaking of the backyard, there is plenty of storage space in the large shed originally built with the home.  Come and embrace the Highland Park Lifestyle.  This up-and-coming neighborhood is a hotbed of revitalization. Enjoy proximity to local eateries, emerging shops, and downtown San Antonio.  Schedule Your Private Tour Today!  This gem won't last long! If you're searching for a move-in-ready, modern home in a dynamic location, don't miss this opportunity. Come see this home today and make it yours before someone else does.
